    "realEnglish": "**Life on Campus**\nBeing a college student is hard work. I don't have a lot of *time to kill* when I can just *kick back* and relax. I always have to *hit the books*. And finals week begins on Monday, so I really have to *stick to my books*. If I *goof off* too much I'll *miss the boat*. So I'm going to *take my time* to prepare for the tests. I'll learn as much as I can *by heart*. If I don't get it I can't just guess *off the top of my head*. I'll *go blank* during the test! But once the test is over, I'll be free for another week. That's when I'll *crash*.",
